title: Classic BACON PANCAKE Recipe | DJ BBQ
description:
What makes a rad pancake? Bacon, bacon and a little more bacon. Oh and a little bit of help from the Mini DJ BBQ.

Get your kids involved with cooking; mash up the bananas, whisk the batter, ladle the pancakes. If my boy Frasier can do it, so can your little'uns!

Just don't forget the bacon!
